Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to introduce Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here today to fulfill our potential to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ourself, and our fellow human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you do that, you can leave the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's wonderful to have you all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bless you all and give great thanks for your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, today's lecture is going to go on over till next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a two-month lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to cover the entire panorama of the human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to wander through the house of mirrors,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a human dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So today's lecture is called The Human Dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will cover quite a few subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because humanity right now seems to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to be lost in the house of mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't tell the reflection from the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And different lights are shown on different mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And people think that what it is is the light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of the image in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can all sit down and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily to strain to understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start with the number one slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how many people here are new?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, some new newsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,New.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll do a quick review of the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you pay attention, you'll see it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you get it, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what more could you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We started out with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For orientation, the map of consciousness, as you're aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the possible levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on an arbitrary logarithmic map of one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So after a considerable research,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we emerged with a map of levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which is concordant with psychoanalytic theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,psychiatric practice, human experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the classic chain of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you research for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness, you'll recapitulate the classic chain of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So on the left-hand side is the way we view God from these various levels, the way we
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,view ourself, and then it has a logarithmic number, and then the emotion that goes with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then over on the right, we have what is the process going on in consciousness at that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is an extremely simple linear, I mean, one to a thousand, it's just like taking people's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature, taking the temperature of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look at these flowers and you say, what is it, what are the temperature, what's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the temperature of those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, they look to me like stunning beauty, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have hay fever, you might say, man, those are ugly, I've got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's the subjective warp, subjective warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,About 55% of people in the United States calibrate below level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So level 200 is, you might call it an alternate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolutionary, we start at the bottom and we move up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's where mankind has evolved up to this particular point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About half.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Half the people in the U.S. cross the line at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and up is truth and various levels of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200 are falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, below 200, the way to stay above 200 is you follow the Ten Commandments and you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,avoid the seven deadly sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty simple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody worries about salvation, that's all you've got to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the Ten Commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And avoid the seven deadly sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Put you right up near the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, how can I get up to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was spelled out thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You avoid cravingness and wantingness, desiringness, demandingness, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You give up pride and the narcissism, the narcissism that it's based on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You give up resentments and angers and you stop craving everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You give up being fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, if you drop dead right now, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I told you, I tried that right in the middle of the South Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There we were about ready to blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says, you know, we might get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, well, so then we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And he looked at me and said, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's called acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we accept that our life is temporal, then we can give up, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of leaving this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you can go all the way down to fear and things that are grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless, apathy, that which is dedicated to evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is hateful, hateful, hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What does hateful look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the Virginia something or other massacre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was done by a fellow named Cho or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And he had a long videotape that he made of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He calibrated five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The lowest one I've gotten so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse than the Green River Killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Green River Killer had it for quite a while, but Cho beat him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you discover you've made a bad mistake, you've got to come around and try it all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the basic orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything and anything can be calibrated on a level of one to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when we're calibrating something, what we are doing is getting its essence, not its appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people still don't get that, that what a thing looks like is not what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The book is not the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The map is not the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can we get to the essence of a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we do the muscle test, what we're asking for is the level of the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We already know what the appearance is, but what is the essence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the muscle response that we get is ultra simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in trying to complicate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is get the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is get the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to understand it, all you have to understand is quantum physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,quantum mechanics, which I'll explain to you in a couple of sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the infinite field of consciousness, which was the light of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of God shone forth, it's infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One cubic inch of infinite space is equal, is greater than,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the total mass of the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One cubic centimeter of space greater than the total mass of the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So in an infinite timeless space, there is no beginning, there is no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no here, there is no there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no now or then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, the field of consciousness is omniscient by virtue of being all that has ever been or can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, the field of consciousness is omniscient by virtue of being all that has ever been or can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, the field of consciousness is omniscient by virtue of being all that has ever been or can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, the field of consciousness is omniscient by virtue of being all that has ever been or can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, the field of consciousness is omniscient by virtue of being all that has ever been or can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,been or can be so when we do essence what happens is we collapse the wave
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,function see in quantum mechanics you have the Heisenberg principle you go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Schrodinger equations of the hypothetical time dependent or time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,independent and then the wave function which is really a mathematical formula
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiates and you can collapse the wave function meaning you go from energy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to particle it was discovered of course in trying to research the basic nature
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of light itself it occurs in waves particles so the potential becomes an
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,actual only if there is a reality only if there is a reality so if I make a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,statement that has a reality to it this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,affects the quantum potential, and collapses the wave function,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the person goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pose a question that is false,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it has no corollary in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it has no power, and it does not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,collapse the wave function, and her arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth makes the body go strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for reasons we've mentioned in previous lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And falsehood does not make the body go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It just does not make it go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer is not yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is always yes or not yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The quantum potential is a yes, collapses the wave function,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,your arm goes strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're asking is yes or not yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or not yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or not yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it even better, you ask permission
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,before you ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I wanted to review the basic concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to mention that I learned it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kinesiology class, but that brought us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of static.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:12:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So kinesiology is now an outward muscle test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be very careful in today's world, as we will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So all right, we'll move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's population.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's population, about 80% of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is below 200, 80% of the world's population.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you're talking about truth and integrity and honesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking about 15% of the world even knows what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, we'll move on to the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the way the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are distributed in the human domain, 15%, 20% rather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the people that calibrate.
